data.description: Located in a great neighborhood, nothing to do but move-in!  This three bedroom, One and 2 half bathroom raised ranch is full of charm and character. The home is warm and inviting. Off the living room is the dining space, and then the beautifully updated eat-in kitchen with granite countertops. A large rec/room with pool table. As you continue on the main level you will find the primary bedroom with its own private 1/2 bathroom and walk-in closet, the remaining 2 bedrooms are generously sized with ample closet space. Lower-level features, laundry room for convenience, family room with propane Fireplace and office area. One-car garage with remote. This home is meticulously crafted to offer comfort, style, and functionality. New Slider, New Deck, New Roof, New Driveway, New Furnace, gutter guards.. Enjoy the low-maintenance exterior, don't miss the chance to make this your dream home sweet home! Schedule a viewing and make this house YOURS!
